api_list.name: View User List
api_list.description: Gets a user’s list of favorite libraries.
api_list.code:
import requests

url = "https://python-libraries-tst.p.rapidapi.com/users/1/list"

headers = {
            "X-RapidAPI-Key": "SIGN-UP-FOR-KEY",
            "X-RapidAPI-Host": "python-libraries-tst.p.rapidapi.com"
        }

response = requests.get(url, headers=headers)
print(response.json())
